item.title: CVE-2021-26558|2024-08-03T20:26:25.540Z -- apache%20software%20foundation -- apache%20shardingsphere-ui
item.description: Deserialization of Untrusted Data vulnerability of Apache ShardingSphere-UI allows an attacker to inject outer link resources. This issue affects Apache ShardingSphere-UI Apache ShardingSphere-UI version 4.1.1 and later versions; Apache ShardingSphere-UI versions prior to 5.0.0.
